<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">No, it is a fiction invented on the day you were born and perpetrated with the collusion of the entirety of humanity with the sole aim of messing with<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">No, it is a fiction invented on the day you were born and perpetrated with the collusion of the entirety of humanity with the sole aim of messing with your head. In truth, not only is there no Huckleberry Finn, there was never a Mark Twain. Of course, because I've now broken the pact I'll shortly be summarily executed. This is my legacy to you, Natalia--the breaking of this horrible illusion.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
